---
import ServiceDetailLayout from "../../layouts/ServiceLayoutDetails.astro";
import { SERVICES } from "../../utils/constants";

const brandService = SERVICES.find((service) => service.slug === "brand-shoot");

// Additional metadata specifically for Brand Shoot service
const serviceMetadata = {
  metaDescription:
    "Rent our commercial-grade sets for Brand Photography in Nagpur. Professional backdrops, product display areas, and versatile spaces at Pixxel City Studio.",
  ogImage:
    "https://images.pexels.com/photos/216489/pexels-photo-216489.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2",
  canonicalUrl: "https://pixxelcity.com/services/brand-shoot",
  keywords:
    "brand photography sets, commercial photo studio, product photography venue, nagpur studio rental, marketing photography space",
};

// Enhance the service object with additional metadata
const enhancedService = {
  ...brandService,
  ...serviceMetadata,
  heroImage:
    "https://images.pexels.com/photos/216489/pexels-photo-216489.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2",
  process: [
    {
      title: "Initial Consultation",
      description:
        "We discuss your brand's specific needs and which of our commercial sets would work best for your product or company photography.",
    },
    {
      title: "Set Selection",
      description:
        "Choose from our professional backdrops, product display areas, and versatile spaces that can be customized to align with your brand identity.",
    },
    {
      title: "Booking & Scheduling",
      description:
        "We help you select the appropriate length of time needed for your brand photography session and secure your booking.",
    },
    {
      title: "Studio Preparation",
      description:
        "Before your arrival, we prepare the selected sets according to your specifications, including any special requests for props or displays.",
    },
    {
      title: "On-site Support",
      description:
        "Our team remains available during your session to assist with set changes, additional props, and any technical requirements.",
    },
  ],
};
---

<ServiceDetailLayout service={enhancedService}>
  <Fragment slot="service-content">
    <h3>Professional Sets for Brand and Product Photography</h3>

    <p>
      In today's visual-centric digital landscape, high-quality brand
      photography is essential for making a lasting impression on your audience.
      Whether you're shooting products, creating content for social media, or
      updating your website imagery, having access to professional sets can
      significantly enhance your results.
    </p>

    <p>
      Pixxel City Studio in Nagpur offers commercial-grade sets and versatile
      spaces designed specifically for brand and product photography. Our venue
      provides businesses with professional environments to create compelling
      visual content without the expense of building custom sets.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/216489/pexels-photo-216489.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
        alt="Professional product photography setup"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3178744/pexels-photo-3178744.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
        alt="Brand lifestyle photography set"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
    </div>

    <h3>Why Choose Our Sets for Brand Photography?</h3>

    <h4>Versatile Commercial Spaces</h4>

    <p>
      Our studio features multiple set options that can be adapted to various
      business needs. From clean white backgrounds for e-commerce product shots
      to lifestyle settings that showcase products in use, our spaces provide
      the perfect backdrop for your brand story.
    </p>

    <h4>Professional Lighting Environment</h4>

    <p>
      Proper lighting is crucial for professional brand photography. Our studio
      is designed with optimal lighting conditions and setups that ensure your
      products and brand elements are captured clearly and attractively.
    </p>

    <h4>Cost-Effective Alternative</h4>

    <p>
      Building custom sets for brand photography can be expensive and
      time-consuming. Our venue offers ready-made professional environments at a
      fraction of the cost, allowing businesses of all sizes to access
      high-quality backdrops for their visual content.
    </p>

    <blockquote
      class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg my-8 border-l-4 border-primary"
    >
      <p class="text-lg italic">
        "We rented Pixxel City's studio for our product line photography and
        were incredibly pleased with the results. The commercial sets provided
        the perfect backdrop for our items, and we were able to shoot an entire
        season's worth of content in just one day. The convenience and quality
        far exceeded what we could have achieved elsewhere."
      </p>
      <cite class="block mt-4 font-medium"
        >— Vikram A., Founder of Stellar Home Décor</cite
      >
    </blockquote>

    <h3>Popular Brand Photography Sets</h3>

    <h4>Product Display Areas</h4>

    <p>
      Our specialized product display areas feature clean, customizable surfaces
      with various background options. These spaces are designed specifically
      for showcasing merchandise with precision and clarity, perfect for
      e-commerce listings and catalog images.
    </p>

    <h4>Lifestyle Environments</h4>

    <p>
      Create context for your products with our lifestyle sets that include
      modern living spaces, workspaces, and other everyday environments. These
      settings help customers visualize products in use and create more engaging
      marketing materials.
    </p>

    <h4>Minimalist Studio Space</h4>

    <p>
      Our clean, uncluttered studio space with various backdrop options provides
      maximum flexibility for brand imagery. This versatile environment works
      well for team photos, corporate portraits, and brand identity shoots.
    </p>

    <h3>Booking Information</h3>

    <p>
      Our venue rental includes access to your selected sets, use of basic props
      and display materials, and studio amenities including changing rooms and
      refreshment areas. Please note that our packages cover venue rental
      only—you'll need to bring your own photographer and equipment.
    </p>

    <p>
      For brand photography, we recommend booking for a minimum of 4 hours to
      allow adequate time for setup and multiple shots. Longer bookings receive
      discounted hourly rates, making full-day sessions particularly
      cost-effective for comprehensive brand shoots.
    </p>

    <p>
      A security deposit of ₹2,000 is required at booking, which is fully
      refundable after your session assuming no damage to sets or equipment.
    </p>

    <h3>Book Your Brand Photography Venue</h3>

    <p>
      Ready to create professional visual content for your brand? Contact Pixxel
      City Studio today to reserve our commercial sets for your next product or
      brand photoshoot. Our team will help you select the perfect package for
      your specific business needs.
    </p>
  </Fragment>
</ServiceDetailLayout>
